Now, I can understand some confusion, especially considering that shout just doesn't seem to carry as far on FV as it does on other servers.  You may very well not have heard a shout from where you were fighting.  After testing it out in Kelethin, we determined that an individual standing at one lift couldn't hear a shout from a person at the next closest lift.  Either way, we're pretty good about these things.<br>
