At first, we thought that your righteous indignation was RP.  If you recall, we appologized for it.  Then you continued, as we healed up, to complain nonstop.  That's when I told you to stuff it.  Not in so many words, but that was the desired content.  Your quote was exactly correct, and I commend you on your memory.<br>
